            {
               "text": "### Prerequisites\n\nThis text will present a new version of the abacus: the version developed in China (Zhōngguó, 中國), before being adopted and modified in Japan (Nippon-koku or Nihon-koku, 日本国). Therefore, we suggest studying the previous text before proceeding with this one (<htcite0>).",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "339c7ff5-8365-49bb-a1cd-ad5a13d5fd86",
                     "text": "History Tracers Team",
                     "page": "Building to count (Soroban, 算盤)",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "2026",
                        "month": "",
                        "day": ""
                     }
                  }
               ],
               "date_time": null,
